1.00	Kuraray	Kuraray	Kuraray Co., Ltd Kabushiki-gaisha Kurare) is a Japanese manufacturer of chemicals, fibers and other materials founded in Kurashiki, Okayama, but based in Otemachi, Chiyoda, Tokyo (Ote Center Building) and Umeda, Kita-ku, Osaka (Umeda Hankyu Building). As of June 2007 , Kuraray was the sole worldwide producer of Vectran liquid crystal polymer (LCP) fibre.	
